# Ad Benchmark — Product Specification

**Glassdoor for Paid Marketing Data**

Version 1.0 | February 2026
Prepared for development handoff to Claude Code

---

## 1. Product Overview

Ad Benchmark is a SaaS application that lets advertisers see how their paid media performance compares to aggregated peers. Users connect their Google Ads and Meta Ads accounts via OAuth, and the platform ingests their performance data, calculates benchmarks by industry and spend tier, and displays the comparison in simple line charts.

**Core value proposition:** "Am I doing better or worse than similar companies spending similar amounts on the same platform?"

### Target Users

- Agency owners managing multiple client ad accounts
- Startup founders / marketing leads running their own ads
- Freelance media buyers benchmarking their work

