## 6. Metrics

The platform stores raw metrics and derives calculated metrics at query time. This avoids stale or inconsistent data.

### Raw Metrics (Stored)

| Metric | Type | Source |
|--------|------|--------|
| `impressions` | integer | Direct from API |
| `clicks` | integer | Direct from API |
| `spend` | decimal | Direct from API (in account currency) |
| `conversions` | decimal | Direct from API |
| `conversion_value` | decimal | Direct from API (revenue attributed) |

### Derived Metrics (Calculated on Read)

| Metric | Formula | Notes |
|--------|---------|-------|
| `CPC` | `spend / clicks` | Cost per click |
| `CPM` | `(spend / impressions) × 1000` | Cost per thousand impressions |
| `CTR` | `clicks / impressions` | Click-through rate (displayed as %) |
| `ROAS` | `conversion_value / spend` | Return on ad spend |
| `CPA` | `spend / conversions` | Cost per acquisition/conversion |

