## 13. V1 Scope — What's In, What's Out

### In Scope (Build This)

- User auth (signup, login, logout)
- Company CRUD with industry selection
- Google Ads OAuth connection + daily data pull
- Meta Ads OAuth connection + daily data pull
- Account-level daily metrics ingestion (not campaign-level)
- Dynamic spend tier (quartile) calculation
- Nightly benchmark aggregation pipeline
- Dashboard with line chart (user vs. benchmark) per metric
- Date range selection (7d, 30d, 90d, custom)
- Company switcher and ad account switcher

### Out of Scope (Future)

- Campaign-level or ad set-level benchmarking
- Multi-user access per company (team features)
- Portfolio view (all companies at a glance)
- Alerts / notifications when you drop below benchmark
- Export / PDF reports
- Billing / payment (V1 is free beta)
- Additional platforms (TikTok Ads, LinkedIn Ads, etc.)
- Custom industry creation by users
- Historical data backfill beyond 90 days

